As a wedding stylist based in Delhi, I want to go all out for my brides, even if I have to try on the outfits for them (btw, I love wearing couture, so it’s a win-win). I want my brides to look and feel the best on their special days❤️
Here, I am shooting this video for my NRI client who has shortage of time and cannot come to India until the last week of October - she’s getting married in November, so that’s quite challenging for me. But #iykyk I love a good challenge 🤭
.

.
